TM TT LUN VN THC S
ti: Kin trc hng dch v v ng dng.
Tc gi lun vn: Nguyn Vn Tun Kha: CH2012A
Ngi hng dn: TS. V Th Hng Giang
Ni dung tm tt:
a) L do chn ti
ng dng cng ngh thng tin i vi cc cng ty l hnh ngy cng pht
trin mnh m nhng ch mi dng li mc xy dng website gii thiu v
cng ty, cc tour du lch. Cc thng tin trong nhng website ny n vi khch
du lch cn t v thiu. Mt mt l do cc cng ty l hnh khng ngun nhn
lc thu thp thng tin, mt khc cc cng ty ny cng cha tch hp nhng
dch v cng ngh thng tin sn c di dng dch v web (web service) vo
phn mm cng nh website ca mnh c c nhng thng tin y nht
cung cp cho khch hng.
Cn nghin cu gii php h tr doanh nghip trong vic thu thp thng tin
v tch hp cc dch v li vi nhau c c mt lng thng tin y nht
n vi cc cng ty l hnh v khch du lch.
b) Mc ch nghin cu ca lun vn, i tng, phm vi nghin cu.
Mc ch
Tm hiu bi ton h tr nghip v cho cc cng ty l hnh, h tr thng
tin im n cho khch du lch
Tm hiu tng quan v kin trc hng dch v.
Tm hiu v dch v Google Map API; tm hiu v dch v gi ch khch
sn; tm v dch v mua v my bay.
xut m hnh tch hp dch v du lch phc v cho cc cng ty l
hnh v khch du lch.
Th nghip di dng website cung cp thng tin im n du lch.
2
i tng, phm vi nghin cu
Vi mc ch trn i tng, phm vi nghin cu nhm ti l nhng
nh pht trin website, phn mm cho cc cng ty l hnh vit nam.
c) Ni dung chnh ca lun vn
Lun vn Kin trc hng dch v v ng dng c chia thnh 3 chng:
Chng 1. t vn v nh hng gii php
Chng ny cp n cc vn thc ti ca vic ng dng kin
trc hng dch v v ng dng ca n trn th gii v Vit Nam. T a
ra nhng vn ca bi ton v cc gii php p dng xy dng bi ton
ny.
Chng 2. Nn tng xy dng dch v
Chng ny tm hiu v khi nim kin trc hng dch v, cc tnh
cht ca kin trc hng dch v, tm hiu v web service, gii thiu v dch
v web google map API, dch v web ratestogo.net, dch v web
tripadvisor.com.
Chng 3. M hnh tch hp dch v l hnh
Trong chng 3 t gi s nghin cu v a ra m hnh dch v web
khch sn, dch vu web nh hng ng thi xy dng m hnh tch hp dch
v web trn.
Chng 4. Tch hp dch v vo website
Trong chng 4 tc gi s gii thiu s website v b cc ca
website, ng thi cng a ra cc kim chng dch v web pha server
d) Phng php nghin cu.
Tm hiu l thuyt v kin trc hng dch v,
Tm hiu v dch v sn c nh dch v web Google Map API, dch v web
ratestogo.net, dch v web tripadvisor.com.
Tm hiu cc cng c xy dng dch v web
